{"questionId":"19196","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Points in the plane are subjected to a transformation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>T</mi></math> in which the point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>)</mo></math> is transformed to the point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;where</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi><mo>'</mo></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi><mo>'</mo></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>3</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Determine the area of this square.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>area of square <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn></math> &nbsp;<em><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><br>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"19196","referenceCode":"20N.1.AHL.TZ0.F_7b.ii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Determine the area of this square.","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","AHL 3.9—Matrix transformations"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}